events.name: テキストバックアップ

parameters: It seems like you won't let me off the hook that easily, huh?

To reunite with a former student in this way... Life is truly
unpredictable.

Good day. It is a great honor to have an audience with the
headmaster of the Magic Academy in a place like this.

Is there some urgent matter for someone as important as you to
personally come here?

Haha... There's no need to pretend. If there are individuals who
leak state secrets to the outside, appropriate measures should be
taken.

Moreover, if the mastermind is our school's student... the
Student Council President and the Second-in-command, there is no
choice but for me to personally intervene...

Long time no see, Lunaroa. I was greatly indebted to you back
then.

And now, 'Second-in-command'... Is that where you belong? What
happened to your determination to revive your fallen family?

My determination has not changed. I will do what I must do for
myself... following my own beliefs.

Hahaha...! It's always a joy to witness the growth of my
students, no matter the circumstances. It seems you have already
prepared yourself for this.

(We can't avoid a fight. This opponent is on a different level
from those we've faced before. Be prepared.)

Haha... How exhilarating. Perhaps I had wished for this to happen
as well. Show me your power...!
